  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 180°C (350°F).",
    "Wrap the reblochon cheese in foil and bake for 15 minutes.",
    "While the cheese is baking, heat the cooking oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and sauté until it's translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Remove the cheese from the oven and let it cool slightly.",
    "Unwrap the cheese and place it on a serving dish.",
    "Drizzle the fish sauce, lime juice, and black pepper over the cheese.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
